ZCZC GE93
EXTENDED OUTLOOK
MONDAY TO THURSDAY
ISSUED BY THE MET OFFICE ON BEHALF OF THE MARITIME AND
COASTGUARD AGENCY AT 162300 UTC
ON MONDAY EVENING A WKN FRONTAL TROUGH IS EXP TO LIE OVER
THE SW OF THE UK WITH A RIDGE EXTENDING SE FM ICELAND
TOWARDS THE NERN ISLES AND ANOTHER WEAK RIDGE EXTENDING
FM THE CONTINENT OVER THE SERN N SEA. THERE ARE STILL
