THIS PERIOD HOWEVER AT PRESENT INDICATIONS ARE THAT
FURTHER FRONTAL TROUGHS ARE LIKELY TO MAKE ERRATIC NE
PROGRESS ACROSS THE UK LATER IN THE PERIOD AS DPN LOWS
OVER THE NW ATLANTIC PUSH A STRENGTHENING SW AIRFLOW
TOWARDS THE UK BY THURSDAY. LOC STRG WINDS ARE EXP OVER
CULLERCOATS AT THE START OF THE PERIOD ALTHOUGH MOST SEA
AREAS WILL HAVE NON-HAZARDOUS WINDS. HOWEVER DURING
